column1: DATAFACTORY AUTOCOMPLETE offers effective assistance with incomplete address data. As soon as your customers enter the first alphanumerical characters in the input field, they will receive up to 15 suggestions for valild German addresses. A total of around 1.2 million different address suggestions are available, including all delivery-relevant streets, more than 16,000 postal codes and destinations, 14,000 cities and 75,000 district names.
